1012
00:41:11,359 --> 00:41:13,639
We have many types of fabrics and silk
to choose from.

1013
00:41:13,640 --> 00:41:14,399
Please come in.

1014
00:41:14,400 --> 00:41:15,278
Zhuzi.

1015
00:41:15,279 --> 00:41:16,400
Take care of our customers.

1016
00:41:16,600 --> 00:41:18,120
