1017
00:41:18,120 --> 00:41:21,559
My father doesn't like to
be touched by others. I'll do it instead.

1018
00:41:22,480 --> 00:41:23,079
Okay.

1019
00:41:23,080 --> 00:41:23,718
Please come here

1020
