1036
00:41:52,159 --> 00:41:52,798
Father.

1037
00:41:52,799 --> 00:41:54,039
Take a look at this.

1038
00:41:54,080 --> 00:41:56,440
You can make a lined robe with it.

1039
00:41:58,600 --> 00:42:00,880
That's great.

1040
00:42:01,400 --> 00:42:03,240
Let's choose this one then.

